{
  "stem": "1684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 338.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And finally, they liquidated-- they wanted to-- the Russian front came forwards, and they wanted to liquidate Plaszow, too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So they took 8,000 women.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was one of-- with the 8,000 women.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they took them-- they wanted to take me, too-- to Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And a Jewish OD man, who knew me very well, from-- from Tarnow, he was-- he was working in Tarnow and then came to Krakow too, with us, so he knew me.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And my husband actually asked the woman I worked with, who was the sister of the Jewish lagerfuhrer, Hillevich, sister, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Schnitzer was her name, Fela Schnitzer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She was a very good friend-- I mean, she seemed to be friendly to me, but when my husband asked her, can your brother take my wife out from the transport, she said, no.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We cannot do anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I saw all these people who were taken out who were working with the Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But the Jewish policeman came with water, and the SS chased him away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But he said to me, these two words, go in the back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They don't have enough room for everybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I came back to Plaszow to the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I was saved again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I worked a little while more, too, for Madritsch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then Madritsch and Schindler were friends, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Schindler said to Madritsch, how about coming with me?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm going to make a factory in Brunnlitz, in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But Madritsch didn't want anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe he wasn't able to do it because he had enough money made already on the Jewish workers, so he said he's not interested.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But Schindler made the factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
